    "source": "Bernegger (1997)",
    "description": "Maxwell-Boltzmann, Bose-Einstein, Fermi-Dirac distribution class",
    "formula": "G(d) = [ln(a + b^d) - ln(a+1)] / [ln(a+b) - ln(a+1)]",
    "parameters": {"b": 2, "g": 3},
    "note": "a = (g - b^g) / (b^g - 1) where b^g = b raised to power g",
